</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_30" id="14v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490068612_7157">Karl Coler </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490071607_7162">hans Rumell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490073792_7167"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490077692_7172"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Vns ıſt fürkumen / wie das etlıche <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490081407_7177">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒü </del> wollen cʒü verkawffen / vnd den newen Cʒol cʒü <expan>Augſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490085442_7182">cʒü geben mainen / von dem ſack / Ɉ <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> /. Nu heiſʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490097222_7190">wir vnd empfelhen ew / daʒ Jr das den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490099872_7195">vnd <expan>kawflewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒü <expan>Auſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> verkündet vnd <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490105132_7205">wegen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490102632_7200">ſagt </ab></add> /. Alſo / daʒ ewr keiner denſelben newen cʒol <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490108032_7210">ſol / welicher Jn aber darüber gebe /. Den wöllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490110862_7215">wir darvmb ſtraffen /. wie vvir dann cʒe rat <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_30_line_1576490113914_7220"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Michael<ex>is</ex></expan> . ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_30" id="14v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Karl Coler, Hans Rumell, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, uns ist fürkumen, wie das etliche
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan> ew wollen czü verkawffen und den newen
                        czol czü <expan>Augsp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> czü geben mainen von dem sack ɨ
                                <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu heiszen wir und empfelhen ew, daz
                        ir das den <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>kawflewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czü <expan>Ausp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
                        verkündet und <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen <add>sagt</add>. Also daz ewr keiner
                        denselben newen czol <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sol; welicher in aber
                        darüber gebe, den wöllen wir darumb straffen, wie wir dann cze rat
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Michael<ex>is</ex></expan> ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
